title: SLS BRICKELL IS BRAND NEW!
posting_body: ['Beautiful 1 Bedroom + DEN,2 Bath.', 'Washer/ dryer in unit,shades & blackouts,porcelain floors thought unit.', 'Indulge in an open kitchen with European cabinetry & quartz countertops,European appliances, Floor to Ceiling walls oftinted glass,spacious walk in closets & expansive terrace.', 'Window treatments in every room as well as porcelain flooring throughout Amenities at SLS Brickell include:State-of-the-Art fitness center, rooftop pool for residents only,spa,pool terrace with 200 foot-long pool & private cabanas,kids room,party room & two on-site amazing restaurants,Italian Filia & fish restaurant', 'Bazaar Mar.Enjoy the Philippe Stark designed lobby & amenities,The JoseAndre, Katsuya and Michael Schwartz restaurants and the unique art pieces', 'For this unit or any other, I can send a full spread sheet,', 'Call', 'Mark Kaufman', 'Velocity Realty', 'show contact info']
